Must read caption 👇

💕Amla, reetha and shikakai hair mask 💕
for shiny, soft and long hair

👇How to make hair mask 👇

1️⃣ To make your natural hair mask you need to crush these three magical ingredients. 

2️⃣ Simply throw them into a blender to make a fine powder. Or You can also buy their powder available in the market. 

3️⃣ You should use all the three ingredients in equal quantity.

4️⃣ To use this mask, take the powder according to the length of your hair.

5️⃣ Now add normal water or rose water to it. Make a thick paste out of it. 

6️⃣ After washing your hair apply this paste thoroughly to your hair from roots to ends.

7️⃣ Keep the paste for 50 to 60 minutes and later rinse it with just water.

8️⃣ You can use this remedy once or twice a week.

Benefits ✅
✔️ Reduce hair fall
✔️Get rid of oily and gray hair
✔️ Prevent rough and frizzy hair 
✔️ Prevent hair growth
✔️ Control dandruff 

➡️AMLA 
amla rich vitamin A and C . Studies indicate that vitamin A has some relation to delaying hair loss. And if that is not enough, amla nourishes your hair follicles and promotes your hair growth.
➡️REETHA 
Reetha is a proven anti-inflammatory herb. This means it can help you get rid of scalp irritation and itchy scalp. There is some speculation that dandruff may be caused due to an underlying inflammation or an infection of the scalp.
➡️SHIKAKAI 
It is an effective hair cleanser and forms good foam for an effective hair wash.
Keeps your hair from being tangled.
It is an astringent which means it removes excess oil from your hair so it is just the perfect herb for people with oily scalp and hairs.
It is a proven anti-dandruff treatment.

Please try it and let me know what difference you have seen after trying it.
I definitely tell you that this remedy will great benefit to you.
Thank you 😊
